1) Short Title, Extent and Commencement:
<br/>
<br/>
(a) These Terms and Conditions be called India (India and World Tourist) Terms and Conditions 2012-13. (b) They 

extend to the India and World Tours organised by the India Tours Pvt. Ltd. (c) They shall come in force from 

9th April, 2012.
<br/>
<br/>
