<br/>
<br/>
(a) Tourist/s means the person in whose Name or on whose behalf Booking and/or registration is made for any of 

India and/or World Tours organized by India Tours Pvt.Ltd. (which expression shall, unless it be repugnant to 

the context or meaning thereof be deemed to mean and include their respective heirs, executors and 

administrators)
<br/>
<br/>
(b) Company means India Tours Pvt Ltd and also includes all its brands & divisions namely K&S, Chota Break, My 

Fair Lady, Honeymoon Special, Second Innings, Jungle Tours, Students Special etc. 
<br/>
<br/>
(c) Tour/s means any India and World Tours organised by India Tours Pvt. Ltd. 
<br/>
<br/>
(d) First day of the tour shall start at any time (i.e. in the morning/afternoon/evening) at the first 

destination depending on the arrival of the respective flight/train/cruise or any mode of transport, same shall 

be in case of the last day of the tour. In other words, a 'Day' shall mean a part of the day or 24 hours or its 

part thereof.
<br/>
<br/> 
(e)Tour Escort / Leader / Manager / Assistant by whatever designation called means a Person designated by 

Company to help / guide / assist the tourist/s in and or during India and / or World Tours Organised by India 

